== Abakwaɛm ==
[[File:Ghana_(1957-03-07_A_New_Nation).ogg|thumbtime=0:43|thumb|Universal Newsreel about the establishment of Ghana in 1957]]
Ndwum a ɛyɛ Ɔman Gana ([[Ghana]]) Nkayan ndwum (National Anthem) no, deɛ ɔdii kan hyehyɛɛ (composed) ndwum no ne Philip Gbeho na nsɛmfua anaa nsɛmkaeɛ a ɛwɔ ndwum a yɛ toɔ n o mu no nso Emmanuel Pappoe Thompson na ɛtwereɛ yɛ.

Wɔn  a wɔn wɔ twi atwereɛ ne akenkan ho nimdeɛ (literally) agyinakuo (committee) a na wɔn wɔ Gana (Ghana) Ɔman panii Kwame Nkrumah dwumadiebea anaa sɛ ɔfese (office) na  yɛɛ nsakra mu (revised) anaa yɛɛ nhwehwɛ mu bio.

Owura Michael Kwame Gbordzoe nso ka sɛ anaa nso gye ma ne ho sɛ, nsɛmfua anaa sɛ nsemkaeɛ a ɛwɔ Gana Nkayan ndwum a seisei anaa mprempren yi yɛ toɔ no mu no ɛyɛ ɔno na ɔtwereɛ yɛ wɔ mmerɛ a wɔn tuu Gana (Ghana) Ɔman panii (president) Kwame Nkrumah abae guuɛ akyire no mu.

Akansie (A Competition) bi kɔɔ so saa mmerɛ no na Kwame Gbordzoe a na ɔyɛ ɔdesuanii anaa ɔsukuunii (student) wɔ Bishop Herman sukuupɔn (college) saa mmerɛ no, ɔde saa nsɛmfua anaa sɛ nsɛmkaeɛ a ɛwɔ Ɔman no Nkayan ndwum a yɛ to no seisei no na ɛkɔɔeɛ,na wɔn faa eno de sii " Lift High The Flag Of Ghana " [Ma Gana Frankaa So Kɔ Suro]  a na ɛno ne Gana Nkayan ndwum a na ɔmammu no nyinaa afa de ayɛ yɛn  deɛ (officially adopted) a y'agyeatomu a na yɛ toɔ  anan mu wɔ mmerɛ a Gana nyaa ne faahodie akyire no mu wɔ Kwame Nkrumah abrɛso.(Kwame Nkrumah's regime).
